"stack/blob/main/tutorials/assets/values-05-cpu-offloading.yaml>`_):"
msgstr "并用 (`values-05-cpu-offloading.yaml <https://github.com/vllm-project/production-stack/blob/main/tutorials/assets/values-05-cpu-offloading.yaml>`_) 替换 Helm 值文件："

